feed.title: GeoConnections CGDI Pilot Feedback Feed
feed.subtitle: This ATOM feed is used by clients to propose changes to the national Geobase Framework database. The national Geobase Framework database is an aggregation or view of a number of provincial databases allowing data to be managed closest to source. Change proposals posted to this feed are monitored by the provinces and territories. Each change proposal is reviewed by provincial custodians who decides how to handle the change request. The dispostion of each proposed change is then posted to the GeoConnections CGDI Pilot Update Feed which can be monitored by clients who have made change proposals.
